data.description: Welcome to your extraordinary two-story home nestled in a beautiful golf course community!This captivating residence offers a perfect blend of elegance, functionality, & versatility, providing the ultimate in comfort & convenience.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living spaces, creating an inviting & spacious atmosphere for entertaining guests & creating cherished memories with loved ones.One of the standout features of this home is the spacious & luxurious primary suite.Not only does it boast a lavish en-suite bathroom & a walk-in closet, but it also includes an adjacent flexible space that can be used as a home office, reading nook, home gym, or even a nursery.This thoughtful addition ensures that your personal needs & preferences are met, making the primary suite a true haven within your home.As you step outside, you'll be delighted to find a beautiful backyard oasis.The vinyl privacy fence ensures a serene & secluded environment, perfect for relaxation & outdoor gatherings.Plus, with no rear neighbors, you'll have an extra sense of privacy & tranquility.The property's value is further enhanced by OWNED solar panels, providing eco-friendly energy solutions & cost savings.Embrace sustainable living while enjoying all the modern comforts this home has to offer.Parking will never be an issue with the convenience of a three-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles, storage, & hobbies.Commute with ease, thanks to the home's prime location with easy access to I-25, Hwy 119, Hwy 52,& Hwy 66.Explore nearby attractions, access essential amenities, & make your daily commute a breeze.This beautiful home with its versatile primary suite offers everything you've been dreaming of & more.Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours & experience the pride of home ownership. New roof as of November 2023! Schedule your showing today & seize the chance to call this marvelous property your new forever home!
